WEBVTT

00:00:53.416 --> 00:00:56.333
Lian Songbai looks decent but is actually worthless.

00:00:56.541 --> 00:00:58.208
He has no real talent.

00:00:58.416 --> 00:01:00.541
Not long after he inherited the Lian family business,

00:01:00.625 --> 00:01:02.458
he squandered it all.

00:01:02.625 --> 00:01:04.041
He came to the manor this time

00:01:04.250 --> 00:01:06.708
to inherit the manor and pay off debts.

00:01:07.541 --> 00:01:09.125
The death of our senior brothers

00:01:09.708 --> 00:01:11.541
was definitely his doing.

00:01:18.958 --> 00:01:21.166
Master, I was wrong.

00:01:22.166 --> 00:01:25.000
I shouldn't have followed Lian Songbai out of vanity.

00:01:25.125 --> 00:01:26.958
And I shouldn't have trusted Gao Li.

00:01:27.333 --> 00:01:30.166
Master, you're all I have now.

00:01:32.500 --> 00:01:34.041
Since you were young,

00:01:34.583 --> 00:01:36.125
the rules I taught you,

00:01:36.416 --> 00:01:37.791
do you still remember them?

00:01:40.416 --> 00:01:42.291
Between master and disciple,

00:01:42.625 --> 00:01:45.333
there should be honesty.

00:01:54.041 --> 00:01:56.166
You are mine.

00:01:56.375 --> 00:01:57.333
Wretch.

00:01:59.166 --> 00:02:01.666
Master, he's a beast.

00:02:01.833 --> 00:02:03.750
Master, I want to stay with you.

00:02:03.833 --> 00:02:05.583
I'll do anything you ask.

00:02:06.250 --> 00:02:07.625
Help me kill him.

00:02:10.625 --> 00:02:11.750
Husband.

00:02:14.000 --> 00:02:15.750
My face...

00:02:18.458 --> 00:02:19.833
Husband.

00:02:21.041 --> 00:02:22.875
What's wrong, my wife?

00:02:24.166 --> 00:02:26.041
Your face hurts, doesn't it?

00:02:26.666 --> 00:02:27.916
What a pity.

00:02:28.166 --> 00:02:29.833
Your face used to

00:02:30.208 --> 00:02:32.375
be worthy of the Lian family.

00:02:32.625 --> 00:02:34.791
But look at you now, so ugly.

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:36.375
You don't still think

00:02:36.541 --> 00:02:38.541
I'll treat you like I did before, do you?

00:02:39.125 --> 00:02:42.708
All I wanted was your face.

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:45.375
I'll deal with you after I inherit the manor.

00:02:46.541 --> 00:02:47.958
Lian Songbai!

00:02:51.333 --> 00:02:53.083
You shameless bitch!

00:02:53.208 --> 00:02:53.791
You...

00:02:53.833 --> 00:02:56.333
Lin Xiaoran already knows about Bai Hua.

00:02:57.666 --> 00:03:00.125
What did you say?

00:03:00.458 --> 00:03:02.875
But I can help you keep this secret.

00:03:03.166 --> 00:03:04.125
Master.

00:03:04.375 --> 00:03:07.333
Don't believe this wretch's lies, Master.

00:03:08.500 --> 00:03:09.833
Teng Rong and the others

00:03:10.000 --> 00:03:12.708
were surely killed by her for the manor.

00:03:13.583 --> 00:03:14.291
Master.

00:03:14.375 --> 00:03:15.416
Lin Xiaoran.

00:03:15.708 --> 00:03:18.041
Lin Xiaoran knows about Bai Hua.

00:03:18.083 --> 00:03:19.041
Master.

00:03:19.416 --> 00:03:21.583
Why are you so nervous?

00:03:21.666 --> 00:03:22.833
It's fine.

00:03:23.000 --> 00:03:25.333
Just let me inherit the manor,

00:03:25.875 --> 00:03:27.875
and I'll take care of him for you.

00:03:39.958 --> 00:03:42.958
Bai Hua's body appeared at the birthday banquet.

00:03:43.125 --> 00:03:46.750
Then, the three dead all had black handprints on their shoulders.

00:03:53.625 --> 00:03:54.541
Oh, I see.

00:03:54.583 --> 00:03:56.250
So the black handprint's purpose is...

00:04:07.000 --> 00:04:07.916
You all...

00:04:08.708 --> 00:04:09.666
Young hero Lin.

00:04:10.083 --> 00:04:11.458
Don't blame us.

00:04:11.750 --> 00:04:14.125
We warned you not to investigate.

00:04:15.625 --> 00:04:18.708
Now you know too many secrets.

00:04:21.458 --> 00:04:22.541
If you keep this up,

00:04:22.916 --> 00:04:24.750
even your master won't spare you.

00:04:25.791 --> 00:04:28.791
But the manor still needs an heir.

00:04:29.208 --> 00:04:32.416
Now, I'm the only possible heir.

00:04:33.666 --> 00:04:34.666
Time to go.

00:04:34.708 --> 00:04:35.833
Wait!

00:04:36.375 --> 00:04:38.583
Don't you want to know who's really killing people?

00:04:38.916 --> 00:04:40.041
If you kill me,

00:04:40.166 --> 00:04:41.375
you'll all die too.

00:04:49.208 --> 00:04:50.333
It doesn't matter anymore.

00:05:12.916 --> 00:05:13.958
Master.

00:05:14.166 --> 00:05:15.833
Are you satisfied now?

00:05:15.958 --> 00:05:17.458
Satisfied.

00:05:20.375 --> 00:05:22.833
Only preserving the manor's reputation

00:05:23.958 --> 00:05:25.500
for you, Master,

00:05:25.875 --> 00:05:27.375
and for the Lian family,

00:05:27.750 --> 00:05:29.625
is truly beneficial.

00:05:30.750 --> 00:05:34.000
If we work together as master and disciple,

00:05:34.416 --> 00:05:36.083
we'll gain both fame and fortune.

00:05:41.416 --> 00:05:42.958
As for that bitch,

00:05:43.166 --> 00:05:45.625
Master, you can use her as you wish.

00:05:45.750 --> 00:05:47.333
I wasn't wrong about you.

00:05:48.125 --> 00:05:49.833
Among all my disciples,

00:05:50.625 --> 00:05:51.875
only you

00:05:53.541 --> 00:05:55.583
truly understand me.

00:06:00.333 --> 00:06:01.791
Master, you...

00:06:03.625 --> 00:06:04.791
Fool.

00:06:06.208 --> 00:06:08.375
If I agreed to your plan,

00:06:09.208 --> 00:06:13.333
I'd probably be your first victim.

00:06:13.916 --> 00:06:18.625
Go die with your fellow disciples.

00:06:24.083 --> 00:06:25.583
My darling,

00:06:25.625 --> 00:06:27.041
go die.

00:06:28.166 --> 00:06:29.750
Old lecher.

00:06:48.041 --> 00:06:51.041
Still not showing up at a time like this.

00:07:10.083 --> 00:07:13.208
I wonder if Lin Xiaoran has caused any trouble here.

00:07:13.375 --> 00:07:14.791
We'll find out soon.

00:07:19.291 --> 00:07:21.458
Officer Li, you've finally arrived.

00:07:21.875 --> 00:07:22.875
Please, come in.

00:07:23.208 --> 00:07:23.875
Let's go.

00:07:23.875 --> 00:07:24.791
Alright.

00:07:29.958 --> 00:07:32.208
How has the manor been lately, Steward Wang?

00:07:32.333 --> 00:07:33.750
Officer Li, you came at an inconvenient time.

00:07:33.791 --> 00:07:35.458
It's the manor master's birthday.

00:07:35.500 --> 00:07:38.625
He took several top disciples out traveling to enjoy the scenery.

00:07:38.708 --> 00:07:41.666
Only this old servant is left here to receive guests.

00:07:42.166 --> 00:07:43.916
I haven't visited the manor in years.

00:07:44.166 --> 00:07:46.416
I didn't expect it to look so renewed.

00:07:47.958 --> 00:07:50.208
Late at night and early in the morning,

00:07:50.250 --> 00:07:52.333
it's the time for men to study.

00:07:52.375 --> 00:07:55.291
The manor master's disciples have all made a name for themselves.

00:07:55.375 --> 00:07:58.041
Even I feel how quickly time flies.

00:07:59.083 --> 00:07:59.875
By the way,

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:01.500
where is my friend Lin Xiaoran?

00:08:02.208 --> 00:08:04.166
Officer Li, you don't know?

00:08:05.125 --> 00:08:08.291
Your friend went traveling with the manor master.

00:08:08.375 --> 00:08:10.666
Didn't he tell you?

00:08:18.791 --> 00:08:20.666
From what I know of Lin Xiaoran,

00:08:20.791 --> 00:08:22.416
he's not someone who breaks his word.

00:08:22.583 --> 00:08:23.833
He had an appointment with you.

00:08:24.041 --> 00:08:26.083
He wouldn't have gone traveling with them.

00:08:26.500 --> 00:08:27.125
Hmm.

00:08:27.166 --> 00:08:28.625
Something's not right here.

00:08:29.333 --> 00:08:30.583
We need to go out and check.

00:08:37.333 --> 00:08:39.041
Officer Li, Lady Shen,

00:08:39.541 --> 00:08:41.875
I've prepared calming soup for you.

00:08:46.208 --> 00:08:47.875
I'll put it in your room first.

00:08:47.958 --> 00:08:49.916
Drink it while it's still warm.

00:08:50.166 --> 00:08:51.125
Thank you, Steward Wang.

00:08:51.208 --> 00:08:52.083
Hey.

00:09:13.541 --> 00:09:14.875
After walking around,

00:09:15.333 --> 00:09:16.875
I feel like this manor

00:09:17.708 --> 00:09:19.083
still doesn't seem right.

00:09:19.708 --> 00:09:22.541
Do you think Lin Xiaoran would really go traveling?